    "rationale": "The credibility assessment team reviewed all thirteen credibility factors. Seven factors were formally assessed; all show achieved levels below required levels for MRL 5. Six factors remain not-assessed due to resource and data constraints. The supplemental mesh-refinement GCI study (see validation result) partially closes the discretization-error gap. On balance, the team accepts the package for submission, acknowledging that open gaps will be addressed in the next assessment cycle prior to regulatory submission.",
